   "author_association" : "CONTRIBUTOR",
   "body" : "Proposal for unit testing on test_framework functions:\r\n1. Use the python `unittest` library instead of TestFramework subclass\r\n2. Put the tests inside the same file as the functions they are testing\r\n3. Use `unittest.TestLoader` and `unittest.TestRunner` to call the tests directly from `run_tests()` inside of `test_runner.py` instead of as BASE_SCRIPTS. No need to change the list of accepted script prefixes in test_runner and no need to make new files.\r\n\r\nMakes these changes for `bn2vch` (followup to [this comment](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/pull/18378#pullrequestreview-377271264)).",
